job description:
Work Requirements

Contractors engaged in this contract will be expected to work within the .NET framework and MS-SQL for application development and:

Provide technical application design, development, testing and implementation servies.

Be available during core business hours at the workstation assigned by ClientI at the Client Application Development work site. Resources associated with this contract are expected to work on-site.

Participate in weekly work prioritization meetings.

Complete accurate estimates for all deliverables assigned.

Complete all development for all deliverables assigned.

Develop test plans for deliverables as directed.

Execute test plans as directed.

Document all development work in accordance with the defined work management process.

Provide technical support to the Client Customer Support Team as directed.Deliverables

OSPI Technical Environment

(1) MSSQL

(2) Entity Framework

(3) ASP .NET 4.0 and above

(4) Object Oriented Programming in C#

(5) TFS and Visual Studio 2010 and above
